        "content": "<p>I was wondering whether it's possible to reconstruct a filter from the neighborhood filters it contains, at least when the filter has a basis of open sets, and allowing the space to be compact Hausdorff?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">topology.separation</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">open_locale</span> <span class=\"n\">topological_space</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">lemma</span> <span class=\"n\">rebuild_le</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">Î±</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">topological_space</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">filter</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">Sup</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"bp\">''</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span> <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰¤</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">})</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰¤</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">intros</span> <span class=\"n\">s</span> <span class=\"n\">hs</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">intros</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">ha</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"n\">ha</span> <span class=\"n\">hs</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">lemma</span> <span class=\"n\">le_rebuild</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">Î±</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">topological_space</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">t2_space</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">compact_space</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- a guess at sufficient assumptions</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">filter</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆ€</span> <span class=\"n\">s</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆˆ</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆƒ</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">set</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">is_open</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆ§</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"bp\">âŠ†</span> <span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰¤</span> <span class=\"n\">Sup</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"bp\">''</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span> <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"bp\">ğ“</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰¤</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">})</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
